channel.title: What is your least favorite Auxy Track you made?
channel.description:
I just wanted to wonder if any of you guys created songs long ago or recently that you dislike. My least favorite track I created was called Steakhouse (IT DOES NOT SOUND LIKE IT IS ABOUT A STEAKHOUSE.) I created Steakhouse the day “Shift” by Tatarat came in the feed (June 11, 2017)
Link: https://app.auxy.co/projects/v_t42skUDigkasgP9fPZAQ==
